## 🚀 About This Repo

```
📦 LeetCode Solutions by Rishi Dusane
 ┣ 📂 Easy/
 ┣ 📂 Medium/
 ┣ 📂 Hard/
 ┗ 📄 README.md
```

This repository contains my **personal solutions** to LeetCode problems, written in clean, well-commented code. Every solution is crafted with a focus on:

- 🎯 **Optimal Time & Space Complexity**
- 📖 **Clear Code Readability**
- 💡 **Multiple Approaches** (Brute Force → Optimized)
- 🔍 **Detailed Comments & Explanations**

