## 💡 My Approach to Problem Solving

```
1. 🔍 UNDERSTAND   → Read the problem carefully, analyze edge cases
2. 🗺️  PLAN        → Think brute force first, then optimize
3. ✍️  CODE        → Write clean, modular code
4. 🧪 TEST         → Verify with examples + edge cases
5. ⚡  OPTIMIZE    → Reduce time/space complexity if possible
```

